    "id": 27,
    "slug": "what-is-the-maximum-hustler-fund-limit",
    "title": "What Is the Maximum Hustler Fund Limit 2026?",
    "content": "<p><strong>Quick answer:</strong> The maximum Hustler Fund personal loan is KES 50,000, with limits starting low and rising as you borrow and repay on time. Beyond the personal product, the bridge loan offers up to three times your assessed personal limit, and the group loan reaches up to KES 1 million for eligible registered groups. The personal loan charges 8% per year, prorated daily, over a 14-day term.</p> <h2>The personal maximum</h2> <p>The personal product caps at KES 50,000. Your individual limit is assessed from your borrowing and repayment behaviour and begins well below the cap, climbing with a track record of on-time repayment. There is no shortcut: consistent repayment is what raises it.</p> <h2>Higher limits beyond the personal loan</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Bridge loan:</strong> up to three times your assessed personal limit, over a 30-day initial term at 8% per year.</li> <li><strong>Group loan:</strong> up to KES 1 million for eligible registered groups, typically over about 30 days.</li> </ul> <p>So the practical ceiling depends on which product you qualify for: KES 50,000 personally, more through the bridge product, and up to KES 1 million as a registered group.</p> <h2>How to reach your maximum</h2> <p>Borrow regularly, repay on time and before the 14-day term ends, and keep your savings portion intact. As your record builds, your assessed limit rises toward the cap. For the step-by-step on raising it see <a href=\"/blog/how-do-i-increase-my-hustler-fund-limit\">how to increase your Hustler Fund limit</a>.</p> <h2>The cost at any limit</h2> <p>Whatever your limit, the personal loan charges 8% per year prorated daily, rising to 9.5% a year if overdue, which keeps it among the cheapest options in Kenya, as our guide to <a href=\"/blog/which-loan-app-has-the-lowest-interest-rate-in-kenya\">the lowest-rate loan apps</a> explains.</p> <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2> <h3>What is the maximum Hustler Fund limit?</h3> <p>KES 50,000 on the personal loan. The bridge loan offers up to three times your assessed personal limit, and the group loan up to KES 1 million for registered groups.</p> <h3>How long does it take to reach the maximum?</h3> <p>There is no fixed time. Your limit rises with consistent on-time repayment and regular use, so it depends on your borrowing history.</p> <h3>Does the maximum change?</h3> <p>Product caps can be revised over time, but the personal-loan maximum is KES 50,000. Treat any much larger guaranteed figure with caution.</p>",
    "excerpt": "The maximum Hustler Fund personal loan is KES 50,000, rising from a low start as you repay on time. The bridge loan offers up to three times your assessed limit and group loans up to KES 1 million. The personal loan charges 8% a year prorated daily over a 14-day term.",
    "metaTitle": "Hustler Fund Max Limit 2026: Key Updates",
